column2: SELECT #*FLOOR (sppParams.l/#) AS l, AVG (z / cos (RADIANS (sppParams.b) )) AS z, STDEV (z / cos (RADIANS (sppParams.b) )) / SQRT (COUNT (*) ) AS err FROM SpecObj s INNER JOIN sppParams ON s.specObjID = sppParams.SpecObjID WHERE s.z between # and # and Feha between # and # and sppParams.b between # and # GROUP BY #*FLOOR (sppParams.l/#) ORDER BY #
